{"tid":1520104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我敢講831既處理比以往所有日子都容易, 你肯出就贏!唔好犯上同樣既錯誤!","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T07:18:56.000Z","uid":196536,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d8384bd0f8378cc320347b8ce44b92e3af1185b6","tid":1520104,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:57:46.000Z","msg":"班仆街講到戒嚴咁<br />\n又高調拉人 議員行人唔關事既照拉<br />\n就係要滅聲 就係要你驚<br />\n你真係驚?咁你就輸啦!<br />\n唔記得機場第一日?講到又斷電又斷網咁 又出防暴又盛<br />\n最尾呢?最尾呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7WVVUf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7WVVUf.png&h=f99a8db6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mOOM2zg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmOOM2zg.png&h=0577c9af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tbNaKNB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtbNaKNB.png&h=e6f523c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n非法集結?咪笑撚死人啦!睇下面個po!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519474/page/1?post=2\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519474/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n唔好比班仆街大到!你肯出就贏!<br />\n<br />\n不過都有野要注意!<br />\n<strong>和理非手足</strong>都要BLACKBLOC<br />\n用太空卡 唔好帶PAYWAVE 信用卡<br />\n熄定位 熄生物解鎖<br />\n諗好換裝安排<br />\n唔好企咁密<br />\n玩少d電話 留意多d四圍<br />\n<strong>勇武手足</strong><br />\nBE WATER 打遊擊唔好圍狗屋唔好留守<br />\n祝武運昌隆!<br />\n<br />\n同埋聽日絕對唔係endgame!咪撚比人帶風向!<br />\n919293都要人!大家量力而為!可以既話辛苦少少!<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">諗下香港, 諗下六個烈士<br />\n諗下爆眼少女同老師, 諗下被斬至傷殘的義士, 被打致重傷既義士, 被性暴力蹂躪的義士</span><br />\n我地唔可以令佢地白白犧牲!<strong>聽日絕對唔係endgame, 但香港人要assemble!</strong><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港期盼香港人會恪守其責<br />\nHONG KONG EXPECTS THAT HKERS WILL DO THEIR DUTIES</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>改自Vice Admiral Horatio Nelson, 1805, Cape Trafalgar</em></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港興廢在此一戰 諸君需奮力迎戰</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>改自Tōgō Heihachirō(東郷平八郎), 1905, Tsu-Shima Strait</em></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">我輩鐵血男兒，決當與敵一拼也</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>關麟徵(國軍二級上將), 1938, 台兒莊</em></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港, 時代革命</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>梁天琦, 2016, 香港</em></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港人齊上齊落, 大事必成!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"aad6ce29a74747df7b26bbea1a5197af8cc48fc1","tid":1520104,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dyrx7H5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDyrx7H5.gif&h=f7c0f28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2fsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=45e13475\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2fsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=2ce161d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2fsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=dbe18c1c\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"51f075c0773b9cb6fd87266a1e6f768aaa8c7b85","tid":1520104,"uid":200021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"scor