;\">我輩鐵血男兒，決當與敵一拼也</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>關麟徵(國軍二級上將), 1938, 台兒莊</em></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港, 時代革命</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><em>梁天琦, 2016, 香港</em></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港人齊上齊落, 大事必成!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T23:46:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6f228e49f33cd11b6706c7e44f1706556d9e666a","tid":1520104,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T04:35:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"636db92c651ca5ed487396be76137aa2ce48fd4b","tid":1520104,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:25:24.000Z","msg":"TUI"},{"pid":"0d6b191e7b85847def21f944f6ad97bb7052d8c4","tid":1520104,"uid":196536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:18:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb3c167aad4b562f56f77ae57dc12152a1deae78","tid":1520104,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"請支持國難五金西環店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1521301/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}